originalText.text:
This dispensary is a new gem among LES. The range of products is impressive, covering everything from flowers to concentrates to edibles and of course the essential tools. You can tell by the atmosphere of the place these guys are about quality. All of their products were grade A and very reasonable priced. The place is strongly air conditioned so that you can view their front display in comfort during these hot summer days. The aesthetic is clean and refreshing with a very urban feel. Definitely the nicest dispensary I’ve been to yet.

Atmosphere: 5/5
Product quality: 5/5
Aesthetic: 5/5
Prices: Great

originalText.text: MOZ is a classy high end dispensary. The bud tenders are super welcoming and detail oriented .. paying close attention to their clients’ needs. Their love for art can be seen right away - the vibes are great and I recommend.

originalText.text:
I recently had the pleasure of visiting MOZ dispensary in LES, and I must say it was an exceptional experience from start to finish. MOZ truly stands out in terms of product selection, atmosphere, and customer service.

Upon entering MOZ, I was immediately struck by the modern and inviting ambiance. The sleek design and clean layout was inviting, which showcased premium clothing and amazing artwork. Their staff was incredibly welcoming and knowledgeable, ready to assist with any questions or recommendations.

The variety of products available at MOZ was impressive. It is evident that they prioritize offering an array of quality products that include flowers, edibles, and carts – something for every preference and need.

All in all, MOZ is definitely a gem for sure!

originalText.text: Was the perfect spot to pregame before hitting up the bars. Been to a lot of dispensaries in the area but the bud tenders really know their stuff. Over 20+ exotic weed strains, dope apparel and local artwork.  If you’re in LES, highly recommend stopping by.

originalText.text: Wow, first impressions are everything. I stopped in to grab some stuff for my partner and as soon as I walked in I knew this place was different. Everything is immaculate and organized with a hint of modern fashion and a vast selection of product. The staff is more than friendly and willing to help find what fits your needs, they are patient and overall great people. In a city over-run with hundreds of pot shops, this one really stands out above the rest from their professionalism, friendly/knowledgeable staff and cleanliness with tested products. Can’t ask for more, highly recommend giving this place a visit!
